edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"所以尋日我都係留過言話<br />\n佢兩個今時今日仲未出過黎講過一句聲<br />\n一係比淋病禁錮左 一係就本來佢地都有啲問題<br />\n邊有可能睇住成件事發展到咁嘅地步仲會堅持為左要推呢條例先還到個公道<br />\n佢地兩個唔撚睇國際新聞？台灣之前啲講法佢地完全唔知？<br />\n如果佢地唔知嘅 咁淋病絕對係最大敵人<br />\n但如果佢地知嘅 佢地嘅沉默就係助長整個政府仆街嘅罪人"},{"pid":"03ad3386e6723794c29911c78f13320963d26c9e","tid":1229052,"uid":96704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"咁既情況應該都係俾中共禁咗聲架啦"},{"pid":"8ab9b478bd5590acf5386e67627532f203debe39","tid":1229052,"uid":7947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"其實...仲有無潘生潘太依兩個人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者會唔會被滅聲了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae8f68da741cf0872566690f0a300c5581243d1","tid":1229052,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人會懷疑佢地係出唔到聲?"},{"pid":"e5151242c2b09c83a64aa9f2e16ec2c39d7a7964","tid":1229052,"uid":70115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:19:50.000Z","msg":"佢不幸地冇左個女已經好慘，唔好再加罪於人"},{"pid":"2d1f4dc23693efa53f51dfaa9a8944730369a8d5","tid":1229052,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"冚家剷！"},{"pid":"32437a57940cc8133aa9f4fab563c0266317d583","tid":1229052,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"拎個女俾政府整饅頭<br />\n都痴線嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3c0fb6d5c77c3dd92afe12a83eb7328a013152","tid":1229052,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">合十雙手去禱告<br />\n人生夢一場革命至蒼老<br />\n難得夢一場革命不老</span></span>"},{"pid":"